&lt;p&gt;The lines b3-b4 contain the quotation and pada-like translation of the first of two famous Udānavarga stanzas, Udv. IV 37 and 38. This is a parallel in Tocharian A texts [[A 258]] a4-a5 and [[A 354]] b5-b6.&lt;/p&gt;</item>
